{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"storage","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/storage_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>storage</code> イベントは、ストレージエリア (<code>localStorage</code> または <code>sessionStorage</code>) が変更されたときに発生します。詳しくは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API\">Web Storage API</a> をご覧ください。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_info","title":"一般情報","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"仕様\">仕様</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><em><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/webstorage/#the-storage-event\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Web Storage</a></em></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"インターフェイス\">インターフェイス</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageEvent\"><code>StorageEvent</code></a></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"バブリング\">バブリング</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">不可</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"キャンセル可能か\">キャンセル可能か</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">不可</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"ターゲット\">ターゲット</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">DefaultView (<code>&lt;window&gt;</code>)</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"既定のアクション\">既定のアクション</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">なし</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"プロパティ","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>The event target (the topmost target in the DOM tree).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>key</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> (string)</td>\n   <td>The key being changed.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>oldValue</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> (string)</td>\n   <td>The old value of the key being changed.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>newValue</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> (string)</td>\n   <td>The new value of the key being changed.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>url</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> (string)</td>\n   <td>The address of the document whose key changed.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>storageArea</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">読取専用 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage\"><code>Storage</code></a></td>\n   <td>The Storage object that was affected.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"一般情報","id":"general_info"},{"text":"プロパティ","id":"properties"}],"summary":"storage イベントは、ストレージエリア (localStorage または sessionStorage) が変更されたときに発生します。詳しくは Web Storage API をご覧ください。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window: storage event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window: storage event","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers.onstorage","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers.onstorage","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"storage","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"storage","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/window/storage_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/window/storage_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Window/storage_event","